snippet.title: L.A. Noire: The Complete Edition Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
L.A. Noire: The Complete Edition is now available from retail stores and digital distributors across North America (look for it Friday in Europe and Australia). In tandem with today's North American release, we present the new official launch trailer for The Complete Edition

See more at www.rockstargames.com/lanoire
